<li>Manage your followers</li>
<li>Assign followers to groups</li>
<li>Assign groups to followers</li>
<li>Group Message: send a message to group(s) you have created</li>
<li>Error checking/reporting when sending messages</li>
<li>Character counts for messages</li>
</ul>

